## The 8 phases (what each one does)

**Planning** (methodology 00-30):
- `00-mapeamento-problema.md` — discovery & problem mapping (via `/scout`)
- `10-prd.md` — PRD gates (via `/plan` + `/attest`)
- `20-stack.md` — stack decisions (archetype defaults)
- `30-skills-agents.md` — skills / agents / hooks

**Execution** (40-50):
- `40-execucao.md` — parallel waves + worktrees (via `/hunt`)
- `50-qualidade-testes.md` — multi-agent review (via `/review`)

**Deploy & handoff** (60-70):
- `60-deploy-infra.md` — deploy with security gate (via `/den`)
- `70-onboarding-time.md` — onboarding teammates (via `/pack`)

Transversal: `materializacoes.md` (tool adapter), `principios-transversais.md` (cross-phase).

## Commands

| Command | Phase | What it does |
|---|---|---|
| `/scout` | 00 | Interview-based discovery |
| `/plan <slug>` | 10-30 | Scaffold spec + plan; attest gates |
| `/attest` | 10-30 | Flip a gate (interactive default) |
| `/hunt <plan>` | 40 | Decompose + worktree dispatch |
| `/gather` | 40 | Merge wave + regression + tag |
| `/howl` | any | State + next action |
| `/review` | 50 | Multi-agent quality review |
| `/den` | 60 | Deploy with security gate |
| `/pack` | 70 | Onboarding guide |
| `/matilha-design` | any | Anti-slop design (frontend only) |

